OL,3,CBritish forces intercept Russian
OL,4,Cshadow fleet vessel in Channel, PM says
OL,6,FThe British armed forces intercepted a
OL,7,FRussian shadow fleet vessel in the
OL,8,FChannel in the early hours of Sunday,
OL,9,Fthe Prime Minister said.
OL,11,FThe Ministry of Defence (MoD) said
OL,12,FRoyal Marine commandos and specially
OL,13,Ftrained law enforcement officers from
OL,14,Fthe National Crime Agency boarded a
OL,15,Fsanctioned oil tanker during a six-
OL,16,Fhour operation ` the first UK-led
OL,17,Foperation of its kind.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/4
