OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1781511482
OL,3,CBritish forces intercept Russian
OL,4,Cshadow fleet vessel in Channel, PM says
OL,6,FThe vessel Smyrtos will be
OL,7,Fprovisionally moved to an anchorage
OL,8,Foff the south coast of England and
OL,9,Fwill be monitored for any
OL,10,Fenvironmental or safety concerns.
OL,12,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,13,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,14,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,15,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,17,FAccording to the MoD, the operation
OL,18,Fwas supported by aircraft from the
OL,19,FMaritime Air Group (Chinooks, Merlin
OL,20,FMk4 and Wildcat), an RAF P-8 aircraft,
OL,21,Fand HMS Sutherland and HMS Ledbury.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/4
