OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1781511482
OL,3,CBritish forces intercept Russian
OL,4,Cshadow fleet vessel in Channel, PM says
OL,6,FSir Keir Starmer said in a statement:
OL,7,F"This operation delivers yet another
OL,8,Fblow to Russia and reminds those
OL,9,Ffuelling (President Vladimir) Putin's
OL,10,Fwar in Ukraine that they cannot hide.
OL,12,F"I want to pay tribute to all those
OL,13,Finvolved, including our armed forces
OL,14,Fand law enforcement officers who keep
OL,15,Fthis country safe 24 hours a day, 365
OL,16,Fdays a year."
