CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1781511482
OL,3,CBritish forces intercept Russian
OL,4,Cshadow fleet vessel in Channel, PM says
OL,6,FDefence Secretary Dan Jarvis said:
OL,7,F"Operations like this require skill,
OL,8,Fprofessionalism and courage. I pay
OL,9,Ftribute to our armed forces personnel
OL,10,Fand all those involved.
OL,12,F"Russia relies on its shadow fleet to
OL,13,Ffund their conflict in Ukraine and our
OL,14,Finterdiction delivers a blow to
OL,15,FPutin's illegal war."
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOUwD@UO]
